      "type": "code",
      "mimeType": "application/vnd.google-apps.presentation",
      "content": "# OncoTrials Network Expansion & Biopharma GTM Deck\n\n> **3.4x Accrual Speedup**: Accelerated point-of-care clinical trial screening across 250+ community oncology practices.\n\n- **TAM & SAM Growth**: Serviceable market reaching 3.5M+ active cancer patient EHR records in real-time.\n- **Biopharma Sponsor Access**: Real-time de-identified clinical evidence streams connecting sponsor protocols to active sites.\n\n---\n\n# Practice Onboarding & Regional Pipeline\n\n## Community Practice Scale-Up\n\n- **Texas Oncology Associates**: 48 Oncologists live on OncoEMR — active CRC workflow training.\n- **Rocky Mountain Cancer Centers**: 24 Oncologists live on OncoEMR — biomarker gateway setup.\n- **Highlands Oncology Group**: 16 Oncologists integrated — staff protocol kickoff scheduled.\n\n## Onboarding Metrics\n\n- **Active Network Sites**: `142 active sites` onboarded (+18 community sites added this month).\n- **Monthly Patient Screening**: `18,450 EHR records` auto-screened with 2,140 point-of-care alerts triggered.\n\n---\n\n# Biopharma Partnership Architecture\n\n## Real-World Evidence & Accrual Gateway\n\n- **Automated Eligibility Checks**: Instant protocol matching reduces patient screening time by `66%`.\n- **EHR Integration Gateways**: Zero-friction HL7 FHIR pipelines connect directly to community practice workflows.\n- **Protocol Velocity Guarantee**: Sponsor partners receive verified eligibility alerts within 12 hours of patient intake."
